{"type":"message","id":"a54abfbc","parentId":"edcf2881","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:31:51.995Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach is asking if I integrated SPARK (the semantic drift/creative writing project) into myself as a personality module. Looking back at the session logs, SPARK was being worked on extensively today — the Drift Chamber / SPARK project had significant progress with the coherence ceiling pushed to 0.471, thematic graph with 217 concepts, and the IMAGINATIVE steering regime. But there's no mention of actually integrating it into myself as a personality module.\n\nI should be honest that it wasn't done — I remember the discussions about it but there's no implementation noted.","thinkingSignature":"afa1e1c97825296926d10886675d7e5eb3662ed56dbb8b478ccd955c5587a533"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No, that didn't happen. SPARK got built out (coherence ceiling at 0.471, demo ready, paperspace notebook spun up) but integrating it as a personality module for myself never got implemented. Still just me in here — vanilla Nova. Want me to take a crack at it tonight or save it for tomorrow?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":190,"cacheRead":16219,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16409,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774236698484}}
