concept and applies it as a living personality layer for me. It's functional, not just planned. There's also a `memory/2026-03-23.md` that looks like a session transcript from tonight with more detail.\n\nAlso spotted: you asked about Telegram webhooks at 22:59 and then \"?\" at 23:15 — did that not get answered? I don't see webhook setup in the logs. Want me to handle that now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15555,"output":480,"cacheRead":12848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774236763263}}
