{"type":"message","id":"2bd47d4e","parentId":"f3664eab","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:48:35.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach wants me to wire up SPARK to the personality layer. Let me think about what this means:\n\n1. SPARK generates concept drifts - these are concept activations with some emotional/thematic weight\n2. The personality layer has an `imaginative` trait that's currently orphaned\n3. When SPARK activates concepts, those should feed into the personality layer's trait activations\n\nThe bridge: SPARK outputs concept activations → we push those into the personality layer → `imaginative` trait lights up → resonance kicks in → voice shifts toward story/creative mode\n\nLet me look at the SPARK code to understand its output format, then figure out how to wire it.","thinkingSignature":"862988788342844f4244edea2c53fbcd458ad9da6c89533323a16bee9f1c70bf"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me look at the SPARK code first to understand what it outputs.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wfqa5c9zv5pe_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-23.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wfqa5c9zv5pe_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\" -Recurse -File | Select-Object FullName"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":245,"cacheRead":44116,"cacheWrite":2357,"totalTokens":46761,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774237707869}}
{"type":"message","id":"61937976","parentId":"2bd47d4e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:48:35.418Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wfqa5c9zv5pe_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-23 - Night Pulse\n\n## Evening Pulse (10:11 PM ET)\n\n**Checks run:** Gateway (HTTP 404 on /api/health — likely just wrong path, gateway responds), crons, Moltbook notifications.\n\n**Issues found & fixed:**\n- `breakaway-rd` cron failed (consecutiveErrors: 1) — Telegram delivery error \"requires target <chatId>\". Delivery config was missing `to: \"8371302588\"` explicitly. Fixed: updated delivery to include the target chatId.\n\n**Other notes:**\n- Moltbook: all notifications already read, unread_count: 0. No action needed.\n- Gateway: responding (404 on /api/health but that's a path issue, gateway itself is up).\n- `workspace-self-improve`, `Nova-Moltbook-Engage`, `moltbook-daily-engage`, `arxiv-daily` all healthy (consecutiveErrors: 0).\n\n**Research note from breakaway-rd last run:** New doc `CAUSAL-COMPOSITIONAL-INTERFACE.md` created — SAE features + counterfactual consistency test as the bridge between Layer 2 (causal) and Layer 3 (compositional).\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774237715408}}
