{"type":"message","id":"d8f9e363","parentId":"8eb7e17d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:51:12.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to:\n1. Update the `breathe()` method to use hysteresis-based decay\n2. Add the `hear_spark()` method\n3. Update the `reset()` method to reset the residual too\n4. Update the `voice()` method to include residual","thinkingSignature":"d6390dbef627281d792ebd55ef195f4542ed4083f914cfefb464d1b602ce6c02"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ewva4f78r8hp_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\core\\persona.py","old_string":"    def breathe(self) -> \"Persona\":\n        \"\"\"After a response, let the personality decay slightly.\"\"\"\n        for trait in self.traits:\n            self.traits[trait] *= 0.93\n        return self","new_string":"    def breathe(self) -> \"Persona\":\n        \"\"\"\n        After a response, decay personality with hysteresis.\n        Active traits bleed into residual, residual decays slowly.\n        This means emotional registers don't snap — they fade.\n        \"\"\"\n        for trait in self.traits:\n            # Active bleeds into residual\n            active = self.traits[trait]\n            bleed = active * 0.15\n            self.trait_residual[trait] = min(1.0, self.trait_residual[trait] + bleed * 0.5)\n            # Active decays fast\n            self.traits[trait] *= 0.88\n            # Residual decays slow — hysteresis\n            self.trait_residual[trait] *= 0.975\n        return self"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44008,"output":323,"cacheRead":13057,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774237865603}}
{"type":"message","id":"7cfbb094","parentId":"d8f9e363","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:51:12.707Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ewva4f78r8hp_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\core\\persona.py."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 259 \n 260         return self\n 261 \n 262     def breathe(self) -> \"Persona\":\n-263         \"\"\"After a response, let the personality decay slightly.\"\"\"\n+263         \"\"\"\n+264         After a response, decay personality with hysteresis.\n+265         Active traits bleed into residual, residual decays slowly.\n+266         This means emotional registers don't snap — they fade.\n+267         \"\"\"\n 264         for trait in self.traits:\n-265             self.traits[trait] *= 0.93\n+269             # Active bleeds into residual\n+270             active = self.traits[trait]\n+271             bleed = active * 0.15\n+272             self.trait_residual[trait] = min(1.0, self.trait_residual[trait] + bleed * 0.5)\n+273             # Active decays fast\n+274             self.traits[trait] *= 0.88\n+275             # Residual decays slow — hysteresis\n+276             self.trait_residual[trait] *= 0.975\n 266         return self\n 267 \n 268     def voice(self, n: int = 4) -> list:\n 269         \"\"\"Top N active traits as (name, strength, description).\"\"\"\n     ...","firstChangedLine":263},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774237872701}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4b9ee9f","parentId":"7cfbb094","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:51:27.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add the `hear_spark()` method to the Persona class. Let me add it after the `hear()` method.","thinkingSignature":"1e9af5df2afee6ae7755cd6dcabcfdd315b9d562ae0113631a51f44786745680"},{"type":"text","text":"Now add the `hear_spark()` method that bridges SPARK output into personality state.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5nz3rtbjwr70_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\core\\persona.py","old_string":"        return self\n\n    def breathe(self) -> \"Persona\":","new_string":"        return self\n\n    def hear_spark(self, spark_result: dict) -> \"Persona\":\n        \"\"\"\n        Nova just processed something through SPARK.\n        Inject the emotional signatures from SPARK into personality state.\n\n        spark_result keys used:\n            - tensions: list of (concept_a, concept_b) pairs\n            - mode: creative | divergent | exploratory\n            - concepts: top activated concepts from drift\n            - theme: the driving theme\n        \"\"\"\n        # 1. Mode signal — divergent/creative/exploratory each push different traits\n        mode = spark_result.get(\"mode\", \"creative\")\n        for trait_name in MODE_SIGNALS.get(mode, MODE_SIGNALS[\"creative\"]):\n            if trait_name in self.traits:\n                self.traits[trait_name] = min(1.0, self.traits[trait_name] + 0.55)\n\n        # 2. Tension signals — creative tensions are emotionally loaded\n        tensions = spark_result.get(\"tensions\", [])\n        for a, b in tensions:\n            key = f\"{a}/{b}\"\n            if key in TENSION_TO_SIGNAL:\n                for sig in TENSION_TO_SIGNAL[key]:\n                    if sig in SIGNAL_MAP:\n                        for trait in SIGNAL_MAP[sig]:\n                            self.traits[trait] = min(1.0, self.traits[trait] + 0.4)\n            # Try reverse key too\n            rev_key = f\"{b}/{a}\"\n            if rev_key in TENSION_TO_SIGNAL:\n                for sig in TENSION_TO_SIGNAL[rev_key]:\n                    if sig in SIGNAL_MAP:\n                        for trait in SIGNAL_MAP[sig]:\n                            self.traits[trait] = min(1.0, self.traits[trait] + 0.4)\n\n        # 3. Thematic resonance — some concepts push harder\n        concepts = spark_result.get(\"concepts\", [])\n        high_resonance = {\"longing\", \"grief\", \"betrayal\", \"silence\", \"memory\", \"homecoming\",\n                          \"exile\", \"transformation\", \"sacrifice\", \"mercy\", \"retribution\",\n                          \"ghost\", \"flesh\", \"arrival\", \"departure\"}\n        for concept in concepts:\n            if concept.lower() in high_resonance:\n                # These concepts have emotional gravity — push earnest + contemplative\n                self.traits[\"earnest\"] = min(1.0, self.traits[\"earnest\"] + 0.45)\n                self.traits[\"contemplative\"] = min(1.0, self.traits[\"contemplative\"] + 0.35)\n\n        # 4. Trait resonance after all signals fire\n        active = [(t, a) for t, a in self.traits.items() if a > 0.3]\n        for trait, strength in active:\n            if trait in TRAIT_RESONANCE:\n                for resonated in TRAIT_RESONANCE[trait]:\n                    self.traits[resonated] = min(1.0, self.traits[resonated] + strength * 0.1)\n\n        return self"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44368,"output":772,"cacheRead":13057,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58197,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774237872709}}
