{"type":"message","id":"db2e5c37","parentId":"a15a337c","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:53:07.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's working. The SPARK bridge correctly activates `contemplative`, `earnest`, and `measured` for exploratory mode + emotional tensions. Now let me also test the hysteresis by running breathe() and checking the residual.\n\nLet me also quickly test that the normal hear() flow still works.","thinkingSignature":"a26c0530e9bfd5b2e374114f1de8ef82c2b980c79af623a9a444b40d6b48da9d"},{"type":"text","text":"The SPARK bridge is working — exploratory mode correctly pulls in contemplative + measured + earnest. Let me also verify the hysteresis holds across turns.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1bsno4j2s1pj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, 'C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace')\nfrom core.persona import get_persona, reset_persona\n\nreset_persona()\np = get_persona()\n\n# Fire a strong signal\np.hear('I am frustrated with this thing I cannot figure out')\nprint('=== After message 1 (frustrated) ===')\nprint('Active:', [(t, round(a, 3)) for t, a in p.traits.items() if a > 0.2])\nprint('Residual:', [(t, round(r, 3)) for t, r in p.trait_residual.items() if r > 0.05])\n\n# Breathe (simulate response sent)\np.breathe()\nprint()\nprint('=== After breathe ===')\nprint('Active:', [(t, round(a, 3)) for t, a in p.traits.items() if a > 0.2])\nprint('Residual:', [(t, round(r, 3)) for t, r in p.trait_residual.items() if r > 0.05])\n\n# Breathe again (another turn passes)\np.breathe()\nprint()\nprint('=== After breathe x2 (residual lingers) ===')\nprint('Active:', [(t, round(a, 3)) for t, a in p.traits.items() if a > 0.2])\nprint('Residual:', [(t, round(r, 3)) for t, r in p.trait_residual.items() if r > 0.05])\n\nprint()\nprint('=== Voice at turn 3 (residual feeds back into voice) ===')\nprint(p.voice(5))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50073,"output":468,"cacheRead":13057,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774237977185}}
