{"type":"message","id":"f85f15e2","parentId":"44a233e1","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:07:17.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Everything is restored. Now let me do a quick status check to confirm the integration is complete and summarize what was built for Zach.","thinkingSignature":"302a4102e6bf73cf0db84c1824db78c1f0cba674ce24ab155c4ceec803c103fb"},{"type":"text","text":"Everything's integrated and committed. Here's the full picture of what's now live:\n\n**What was built:**\n\n**`core/persona.py`** — the living personality layer:\n- `on_message(text)` → voice guide shaped by conversation signals\n- `on_spark(result)` → SPARK emotional output feeds into personality state\n- `run_spark(theme, mode, domain)` → one-call SPARK integration (drift + personality in one shot)\n- `after_response()` → hysteresis decay (traits fade, they don't snap)\n- Trait resonance: sardonic ↔ wry, warm → earnest → grounded, etc.\n- 20 creative tension pairs mapped to personality signals\n- `imaginative` trait finally wired up\n\n**`hooks/persona-voice/`** — fires on `message:preprocessed`, stages the enriched message to `memory/persona-inbound.md` so the agent picks it up pre-response\n\n**`AGENTS.md`** — updated with full persona system docs, session startup calls `reset_persona()`\n\n**`TOOLS.md`** — Telegram webhook + cloudflared tunnel details logged\n\n**The pipeline now works like this:**\n1. Message arrives → hook stages it\n2. Nova's turn starts → `on_message()` fires → voice guide shapes response\n3. Response sent → `after_response()` decays traits with hysteresis\n4. If SPARK fires → `on_spark()` feeds tensions/mode/concepts into the same trait state\n\nIt's integrated. It's wired. It runs every turn without being asked. ✨"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79827,"output":348,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774238828262}}
